1
00:00:00,087 --> 00:00:00,812
In this lecture

2
00:00:01,262 --> 00:00:02,538
we will explore Docker

3
00:00:03,025 --> 00:00:04,388
a platform used to develop

4
00:00:04,662 --> 00:00:05,075
ship

5
00:00:05,350 --> 00:00:07,425
and run applications inside containers

6
00:00:07,812 --> 00:00:11,750
